---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout
  title="🤝 Why Sponsor? - Manuel Gil - Software Developer & Open Source Advocate"
  description="Sponsoring my work means directly supporting open-source innovation and developer empowerment."
  keywords="sponsor, open source, developer, innovation"
>
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 pt-20">
    <section class="flex items-center justify-center py-28">
      <div class="max-w-3xl text-center">
        <h1
          class="mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-accent bg-clip-text text-6xl font-bold text-transparent"
        >
          Why Sponsor?
        </h1>
        <p class="mb-8 text-xl text-zinc-400">
          Sponsoring my work means directly supporting <strong class="text-zinc-200"
            >open-source innovation</strong
          > and <strong class="text-zinc-200">developer empowerment</strong>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mx-auto mb-32 max-w-3xl">
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <h2 class="mb-6 text-4xl font-bold">🎯 Sponsors Get</h2>
        <ul class="mb-6 space-y-2 text-zinc-400">
          <li>
            <span class="mr-2 text-primary">▹</span>
            🚀 <strong class="text-zinc-200">Direct Impact on Innovation:</strong> – Your support lets
            me focus on developing and maintaining tools that empower developers and solve real-world
            challenges.
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="mr-2 text-primary">▹</span>
            🏆 <strong class="text-zinc-200">Public Recognition:</strong> Enjoy prominent acknowledgment
            on my website, in project READMEs, and via social media shoutouts that highlight your commitment
            to fostering innovation.
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="mr-2 text-primary">▹</span>
            🔓 <strong class="text-zinc-200">Exclusive Early Access:</strong> Depending on your tier,
            receive early notifications on beta releases, feature updates, and behind-the-scenes development
            insights.
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="mr-2 text-primary">▹</span>
            🧭 <strong class="text-zinc-200">Influence on the Roadmap:</strong> Participate in occasional
            polls and surveys that allow you to help shape future projects and prioritize features.
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="mr-2 text-primary">▹</span>
            🤝 <strong class="text-zinc-200">Community Connection:</strong> Gain entry to an exclusive
            communication channel where you can share ideas, provide feedback, and connect directly with
            me and other supporters.
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mb-6 text-zinc-400">
          Every sponsor is a vital partner in this journey, contributing to a collaborative
          ecosystem that drives continuous improvement and sustainable growth.
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://github.com/sponsors/ManuelGil"
          class="inline-block text-primary transition-colors hover:text-primary-dark"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          Become a Sponsor Today →
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
